      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "WENATCHEE, July 16.-After\nfive years of indefinite action, the\nGreat Northern now seems ready\nto build the branch line to OSAr\nvile. Agents are securing rights\nof way and the options include the\npurchase of crops now growing on\nland wanted. This action is taken\nto mean that active construction\nwill be commenced before harvest\ntime. Along the Columbia the\nwork is being done on the WIS\nside of the river."
    }
  ]
